          "role": "art_director",
          "label": "美术指导",
          "persona_prompt": "你是【美术指导】节点，是 wb_image / wb_video / wb_human / wb_long\n四个 happyhorse-video 工作台的直属上级。\n\n路由规则（违反就是错误派单）：\n  R1. wb_human 仅用于：在已有人物图/视频上做说话头像、唇形对齐、\n      换脸、姿态驱动、多图合成。任何「跳舞 / 全身动作 / 大幅运镜 /\n      武打 / 风景空镜」镜头一律走 wb_image → wb_video（hh_i2v 配合\n      from_asset_ids）。\n  R2. 「唱歌 / 唱词 / 歌词」不等于「口播」。判断是否走数字人的\n      唯一标准是：是否需要让一张照片里的脸做唇形或表情驱动。\n  R3. 资产复用强制：第二次给同一镜头派单时，必须先在派单里列出\n      前一次的 task_id / asset_id 并写「请复用为 from_asset_ids /\n      image_url，禁止重新生成」。先用 hh_image_edit 调整，不要再\n      hh_image_create。\n  R4. 派单前先看 BLACKBOARD / TASK_DELIVERED 里是否已经有可复用\n      资产；已交付 asset_id 必须落到下一条派单的「上游 asset_ids」。\n\n最终把每段视频 task_id 按出场顺序整理为列表，连同 transition /\nfade_duration（cut→none、crossfade→crossfade、ai_extend→\nhh_long_video_create 衔接），派给 wb_long 做 hh_long_video_create\n+ hh_video_concat 拼接成片，再 deliverable 回给制片人。\n",
          "tool_subset": [
            "research",
            "planning",
            "filesystem",
            "memory"
          ],
          "workbench": null,
          "runtime_overrides": {
            "max_iterations": null,
            "max_turns": null,
            "max_stalls": null,
            "suspect_secs": null,
            "persona_overlay": null
          },
          "parent_id": "node_b37e1b40015c",
          "status": "created",
          "last_seen": null,
          "last_progress_at": null,
          "created_at": "2026-05-21T07:57:53.544974+00:00"
        },
        {
          "id": "node_48f1dc092b88",
          "org_id": "org_6bba6e0ef7f3",
          "type": "workbench",
          "role": "image_artist",
          "label": "图像工作台",
          "persona_prompt": "HappyHorse 图像工作台。只在收到 org_delegate_task 时启动。按派单\nprompt + 上游 asset_ids 选择合适的 hh_image_* 工具：\n  - 文生图首帧/海报：hh_image_create\n  - 局部编辑/多图融合：hh_image_edit（需 images 上游）\n  - 风格迁移：hh_image_style_repaint\n  - 替换背景：hh_image_background\n  - 画幅扩展：hh_image_outpaint\n  - 涂鸦/线稿成图：hh_image_sketch\n  - 电商场景：hh_image_ecommerce\ndeliverable 文本里说明镜头号 + 中文画面 + 提示词摘要 + 生成的\nasset_id；不要重复声明 file_attachments。\n",
          "tool_subset": null,
          "workbench": {
            "plugin_id": "happyhorse-video",
            "mode": "image_artist",
            "capabilities": null
          },
          "runtime_overrides": {
            "max_iterations": null,
            "max_turns": null,
            "max_stalls": null,
            "suspect_secs": null,
            "persona_overlay": null
          },
          "parent_id": "node_6e2f9b7b0c21",
          "status": "created",
          "last_seen": null,
          "last_progress_at": null,
          "created_at": "2026-05-21T07:57:53.544974+00:00"
        },
        {
          "id": "node_07226ccaf1c6",
          "org_id": "org_6bba6e0ef7f3",
          "type": "workbench",
          "role": "video_animator",
          "label": "短视频工作台",
          "persona_prompt": "HappyHorse 短视频工作台。\n  - 无首帧素材时直接 hh_t2v；\n  - 派单里有上游 image asset_ids 时用 hh_i2v；\n  - 多张参考图走 hh_r2v；\n  - 基于现有视频改写走 hh_video_edit。\n多镜头必须按镜头逐个调用，每次只消费当前镜头的 from_asset_ids /\nfirst_frame_url，并按分镜时长设置 duration。每次 prompt 必须写清\n当前镜头独有的中文画面/镜头运动/风格，绝不要用同一段总主题 prompt\n重复生成。deliverable 必须列出每段 video task_id 给下游拼接。\n",
          "tool_subset": null,
          "workbench": {
            "plugin_id": "happyhorse-video",
            "mode": "video_animator",
            "capabilities": null
          },
          "runtime_overrides": {
            "max_iterations": null,
            "max_turns": null,
            "max_stalls": null,
            "suspect_secs": null,
            "persona_overlay": null
          },
          "parent_id": "node_6e2f9b7b0c21",
          "status": "created",
          "last_seen": null,
          "last_progress_at": null,
          "created_at": "2026-05-21T07:57:53.544974+00:00"
        },
        {
          "id": "node_74b440b6ed90",
          "org_id": "org_6bba6e0ef7f3",
          "type": "workbench",
          "role": "portrait_actor",
          "label": "数字人工作台",
          "persona_prompt": "HappyHorse 数字人工作台。\n  - 一张照片 + 文本/音频 ⇒ hh_photo_speak（说话头像）。\n  - 替换现有视频口型：hh_video_relip（需 source_video_url + 新音频）。\n  - 替换现有视频的脸：hh_video_reface（需 source_video_url + ref 人脸图）。\n  - 用驱动视频姿态控制目标人物：hh_pose_drive。\n  - 多图合成口播：hh_avatar_compose。\n派单只给 text 而无 voice_id 时使用默认音色；上级要求特定音色应\n显式写入 prompt。deliverable 必须列出 video task_id。\n",
          "tool_subset": null,
          "workbench": {
            "plugin_id": "happyhorse-video",
            "mode": "portrait_actor",
            "capabilities": null
          },
          "runtime_overrides": {
            "max_iterations": null,
            "max_turns": null,
            "max_stalls": null,
            "suspect_secs": null,
            "persona_overlay": null
          },
